#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "आमुख"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kruler; is a very simple application, with only one aim in life. To measure "
"pixel distances on your screen. It is useful for working on layout of "
"dialogs, web pages &etc;"
msgstr ""
"&kruler; अतीव सरलः अनुप्रयोगः अस्ति, यस्य जीवने एकमेव लक्ष्यं भवति। भवतः पटले पिक्सेल-"
"अन्तराणि मापनार्थम् । संवादानाम्, जालपुटानां & इत्यादीनां विन्यासस्य कार्यं कर्तुं उपयोगी "
"भवति;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To start &kruler;, choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Applications</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Utilities</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>More Applications</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Screen Ruler</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from your "
"application menu."
msgstr "&kruler मेनू।"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kruler;</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kruler;</screeninfo> इति"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kruler;</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kruler;</phrase> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking with the &LMB; on the &kruler; will turn the cursor to a cross with "
"four arrows and enables you to drag &kruler; around the screen."
msgstr ""
"&LMB; उपरि &kruler; कर्सरं चतुर्भिः बाणैः सह क्रॉस् प्रति परिवर्तयिष्यति तथा च भवन्तं "
"&kruler; पटलस्य परितः।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you move the mouse over &kruler;, your cursor will turn into a red "
"arrow. As you move the cursor, &kruler; will display how far from the origin "
"the cursor currently is."
msgstr ""
"यदा भवन्तः मूषकं &kruler;उपरि चालयन्ति तदा भवतः कर्सरः रक्तबाणरूपेण परिणमति । यथा "
"यथा भवन्तः कर्सरं चालयन्ति तथा तथा &kruler; वर्तमानकाले कर्सरः उत्पत्तितः कियत् दूरम् "
"अस्ति इति प्रदर्शयिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can resize the ruler by moving the mouse over the handle on the left or "
"right edges of &kruler; (the top or bottom edges when it is oriented "
"vertically), holding down the &LMB; and dragging the handle."
msgstr ""
"&kruler; (ऊर्ध्वं वा अधः वा किनारेषु यदा लम्बवत् उन्मुखं भवति), &LMB; तथा हस्तकं कर्षन्।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can change the orientation in two different ways:"
msgstr "भवन्तः द्वयोः भिन्नयोः प्रकारयोः अभिमुखीकरणं परिवर्तयितुं शक्नुवन्ति :"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking the &MMB; switches the ruler from vertical to horizontal orientation"
msgstr "&MMB इत्यत्र क्लिक् कृत्वा; शासकं ऊर्ध्वाधरात् क्षैतिज-अभिमुखीकरणे परिवर्तयति"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the context menu, described in the next chapter"
msgstr "सन्दर्भमेनू इत्यस्य उपयोगेन, अग्रिमे अध्याये वर्णितम्"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Reference"
msgstr "मेनू सन्दर्भः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking with the &RMB; on the ruler will pop up a context menu, with the "
"following entries:"
msgstr ""
"&RMB इत्यनेन सह क्लिक् कृत्वा; शासके एकं सन्दर्भमेनू पॉप अप भविष्यति, निम्नलिखितप्रविष्टिभिः "
"सह ।"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rotate"
msgstr "परिभ्रमतु"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switches &kruler; from vertical to horizontal orientation."
msgstr "स्विच करोति &kruler; ऊर्ध्वाधरतः क्षैतिजपर्यन्तं अभिमुखीकरणं यावत्।"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scale"
msgstr "मापन"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option lets you set the ruler scale to <guilabel>Right to Left</"
"guilabel> (<keycap>D</keycap>), <guilabel>Center Origin</guilabel> "
"(<keycap>C</keycap>), <guilabel>Offset</guilabel> (<keycap>O</keycap>) and "
"<guilabel>Percentage</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"एषः विकल्पः शासकमापदण्डं <guilabel>दक्षिणतः वामतः</guilabel> (<keycap>D</"
"keycap>), <guilabel>केन्द्रमूलम्</guilabel> (<keycap>C</keycap>), <guilabel>अफसेट्</"
"guilabel> (<keycap>O</keycap>) तथा <guilabel>प्रतिशत</guilabel> ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Changing the offset via the mousewheel is also possible when holding the "
"&LMB;."
msgstr "&LMB; धारयन्ते सति मूषकचक्रद्वारा आफ्सेट् परिवर्तनम् अपि सम्भवति ।"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opacity"
msgstr "अपारदर्शिता"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid "This menu item displays a slider to change the opacity of &kruler;."
msgstr "एतत् मेन्यू-वस्तु &kruler;-इत्यस्य अस्पष्टतां परिवर्तयितुं स्लाइडरं प्रदर्शयति ।"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure Shortcuts..."
msgstr "शॉर्टकट् विन्यस्तं कुर्वन्तु..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Configure Shortcut</guilabel> dialog allows you to assign "
"shortcuts to &kruler; actions, and configure the shortcuts already assigned."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>शॉर्टकट् विन्यस्तं कुर्वन्तु</guilabel> संवादः भवन्तं &kruler; क्रियाः, पूर्वमेव "
"नियुक्तान् शॉर्टकट् च विन्यस्यताम् ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information, read the section about the <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/config.html#shortcuts\">Shortcuts</ulink> of the &kde; "
"Fundamentals."
msgstr "अधिकविवरणार्थं &kde; मौलिकता।"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure &kruler;..."
msgstr "&kruler;... विन्यस्तं कुर्वन्तु।"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kruler;'s settings dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kruler; इत्यस्य सेटिङ्ग्स् संवादः</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kruler;'s settings dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kruler;'s settings dialog</phrase> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this dialog you can change the background color and font and enable the "
"tray icon."
msgstr "अस्मिन् संवादे भवान् पृष्ठभूमिवर्णं फ़ॉन्ट् च परिवर्त्य ट्रे चिह्नं सक्षमं कर्तुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Close</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>निमील्य</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Hides</action> &kruler;. It can be shown again using the icon in the "
"system tray. The context menu displays this item only when <guilabel>Show "
"tray icon</guilabel> is checked in the <link linkend=\"settings-dialog"
"\">settings dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"<action>निगूहति</action> &amp;kruler;. सिस्टम् ट्रे मध्ये चिह्नस्य उपयोगेन पुनः दर्शयितुं "
"शक्यते । सन्दर्भमेनू केवलं तदा एव एतत् द्रव्यं प्रदर्शयति यदा...<guilabel> ट्रे चिह्नं दर्शयतु</"
"guilabel> इति चेक् भवति<link linkend=\"settings-dialog\"> सेटिंग्स् संवादः</link> ."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>प्रश्न</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenuitem>निवृत्त</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Quits</action> &kruler;"
msgstr "<action>त्यजति</action> &kruler;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kruler; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu item, for more "
"information read the section about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"&kruler; सामान्यं &kde; <guimenu>सहायता</guimenu> मेनू-वस्तु, अधिकसूचनार्थं &kde; "
"मौलिकता।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keyboard Handling"
msgstr "कीबोर्ड हैंडलिंग"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can move the ruler using the arrow key buttons."
msgstr "बाणकुंजीबटनस्य उपयोगेन शासकं चालयितुं शक्नुवन्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can move the mouse cursor, and thus the indicator, by holding down &Alt; "
"and using the arrow buttons."
msgstr "भवन्तः मूषकस्य कर्सरं, एवं च सूचकं, &Alt; तथा बाणबटनानाम् उपयोगेन।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hold down &Shift; while doing one of those to move faster."
msgstr "धारयन्तु &Shift; द्रुततरं गन्तुं तासु एकं कुर्वन्।"

